{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idd215770f-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s4145"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4145"},"text":"§ 4145.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Application of other laws","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"To the extent they are not inconsistent with the provisions of this subchapter, the following provisions of subchapter I and title I of the International Claims Settlement Act of 1949, as amended [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s1621"},"text":"22 U.S.C. 1621","children":[],"tail":" et seq.], shall apply to this subchapter: The first sentence of subsection (b) of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t50/s4101"},"text":"section 4101 of this title","children":[],"tail":", all of subsection (c) of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t50/s4101"},"text":"section 4101 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t50/s4109"},"text":"section 4109 of this title","children":[],"tail":", and subsections (c), (d), (e), and (f) of section 7 of the International Claims Settlement Act of 1949, as amended ["},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s1626"},"text":"22 U.S.C. 1626","children":[],"tail":"]."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idd2157710-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1948-07-03/ch826"},"text":"July 3, 1948, ch. 826","children":[],"tail":", title II, § 215, as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/87/846/tI/s103"},"text":"Pub. L. 87–846, title I, § 103","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1962-10-22"},"text":"Oct. 22, 1962","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/76/1112"},"text":"76 Stat. 1112","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idd2157711-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idd2157712-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idd2157713-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subchapter I, referred to in text, was in the original “title I of this Act”, meaning title I of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1948-07-03/ch826"},"text":"act July 3, 1948, ch. 826","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/62/1240"},"text":"62 Stat. 1240","children":[],"tail":", which is classified principally to subchapter I (§ 4101 et seq.) of this chapter. For complete classification of title I to the Code, see Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The International Claims Settlement Act of 1949, referred to in text, is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1950-03-10/ch54"},"text":"act Mar. 10, 1950, ch. 54","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/64/12"},"text":"64 Stat. 12","children":[],"tail":". Title I of the Act is classified generally to subchapter I (§ 1621 et seq.) of chapter 21 of Title 22, Foreign Relations and Intercourse. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s1621"},"text":"section 1621 of Title 22","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"idd2157714-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section was formerly classified to section 2017n of the former Appendix to this title prior to editorial reclassification and renumbering as this section.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
